{"tid":2261011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：食肆6人限聚4人　不認為邏輯不一致","createTime":"2020-10-28T04:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:13:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4df7d092ce76900e344e3071630a8c45404658d2","tid":2261011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】食肆由周五起放寬至最多六人一枱，但限聚令仍維持四人。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始不認為邏輯不一致，相信警方執法時會講道理。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「（吃飯一同走也算常見，是否要不如你們先走？理論上一定要分開？）大家也會從務實做法，比如在短時間有人群聚或是排隊，都不算違反限聚令，從執法角度，會講道理。不同意邏輯不一致，整體來說，需要逐步放寬。」<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又說會繼續審視疫情發展，不排除進一步放寬包括限聚令的社交距離措施。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府計劃在四區設檢測中心，陳肇始說，一旦出現第四波疫情，可以供市民參與檢測，及早找出社區傳播鏈；若疫情持續平穩，亦可為有意出行的市民提供付費的檢測服務。"},{"pid":"edb89fc8f031aafbb64553a6dc8bd36727db1e7c","tid":2261011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=410708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410708&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7EBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7c35a04e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410708&h=095a9d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=410708</a>"},{"pid":"c16ff1debb29850a294b9f14e5d46757d799be78","tid":2261011,"uid":193077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:29:56.000Z","msg":"是但啦。"},{"pid":"369c59d7f765dc2b04cf33bcd79c4f31b1427c39","tid":2261011,"uid":322965,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"係唔係暗示緊六四<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25be06c86c4d2296b8380cd05de22ff312e94bbd","tid":2261011,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"傻閪咪覺得無問題。<br />\n咁佢真係傻閪呀麻。"},{"pid":"00d39e26c8485b20885d6f265bf3c07d61636648"